## Summary

Detail-oriented materials and production coordinator with experience in ERP
systems, BOM validation, inventory reconciliation, and cross-functional
coordination in regulated manufacturing environments. Comfortable working
across engineering, QA, purchasing, and production teams to keep jobs on
track and data accurate. Stays organized and communicates clearly when
priorities shift fast.

---

## Skills

- **ERP Systems:** Epicor, ENOVIA, SQL-based systems; job creation and
  management, inventory tracking, job check-in/check-out, PO tracking
- **Materials & Production:** BOM validation, inventory reconciliation,
  shortage identification, PO coordination, incoming material QA
- **Data & Reporting:** Excel (pivot tables, VLOOKUPs), Tableau, SQL;
  production status tracking and stakeholder reporting
- **Documentation & Compliance:** SOPs, lifecycle traceability, change
  control, QA documentation
- **Cross-Functional Coordination:** Engineering, purchasing, production,
  warehouse, and QA teams

